Step 1: Ansible is available in redhat's epel repository hence first we will install the epel repository.
Command: *yum install epel-release*

Step 2: After installing epel repository we will install ansible
Command: *yum install ansible*

Step 3: Check ansbile version to see ansible installed properly or not
Command: *ansible --version*

Now ansible is installed successfully, next we will configure its files to make it ready for use.
